{"tid":1493892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"投訴話女義士個物理治療師袁子威得到既回覆竟然係咁","createTime":"2019-08-21T12:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T10:11:25.000Z","uid":287755,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1fc7d15029d7b32a3076ef631954658479ecb7","tid":1493892,"uid":287755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月黎成日寫信投訴<br />\n都未見過咁串嘴既回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hjUvfEb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhjUvfEb.jpg&h=b6ebb9aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如初步調查小組於審議有關投訴後決定須轉呈委員會進行紀律研訊，委員會可能會根據條例第23(1)(b)條在進行紀律研訊時傳召投訴人作證，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">並向投訴人作出訊問。條例第23(3)(a)條訂明任何被委員會傳召在研訊中作證的人拒絕出席研訊，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處罰款$500及監禁3個月。 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5O72hy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5O72hy.png&h=3b918621&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qS9frKe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqS9frKe.png&h=ec928304&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7edabdc1826716974b90017c1e94aa240bb67e9d","tid":1493892,"uid":287755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ae2d37ad395e0473f79ad9b8378e20c24bb23d","tid":1493892,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:17:14.000Z","msg":"驚西咩 係條人自己寫出黎"},{"pid":"1c20019e79cdd4ca2de2ff2a50d48d60b1172894","tid":1493892,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚西咩 係條<span style=\"color: red;\">人</span>自己寫出黎</blockquote><br />\n友"},{"pid":"d4535c334eaf2dc05142d324783af364d0965426